WEBVTT

00:05:59.720 --> 00:06:02.160
I was very ambivalent about my experience.

00:06:03.120 --> 00:06:05.720
On the one hand, I really liked Ingolf.

00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:10.160
He was easy and pleasant to talk to,

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:12.976
but on the other hand,

00:06:13.000 --> 00:06:17.696
I couldn't stand the idea
of having so much in common

00:06:17.720 --> 00:06:20.920
with someone who had
such clearly racist views.

00:06:24.080 --> 00:06:25.296
Gradually,

00:06:25.320 --> 00:06:27.016
and painfully,

00:06:27.040 --> 00:06:28.296
I came to realize

00:06:28.320 --> 00:06:33.200
that I had been just as judgmental
of those who had sent me hate mails